definition: to divide/to separate/to distribute/to allocate/to distinguish (good and bad)/part or subdivision/fraction/one tenth (of certain units)/unit of length equivalent to 0.33 cm/minute (unit of time)/minute (angular measurement unit)/a point (in sports or games)/0.01 yuan (unit of money)
one/1/single/a (article)/as soon as/entire/whole/all/throughout/"one" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 1)/also pr. [yao1] for greater clarity when spelling out numbers digit by digit

sentences.english: Melon's skin is thin, only about one-third of thick watermelon rind.
sentences.chinese: 哈密瓜的皮很薄，大約只有西瓜皮的三分之一厚。

sentences.english: Today one-third of the people on Greenland earn their living in the fishing industry.
sentences.chinese: 今天格陵蘭島上有三分之一的人在捕魚業中謀生。

sentences.english: They docked a third of his wages.
sentences.chinese: 他們扣掉他三分之一工資。

sentences.english: About one-third had previously been sexually active.
sentences.chinese: 其中大概有三分之一的人在此之前有過性活躍狀態。

sentences.english: The book, which he borrowed from me yesterday, cost 1/3 of my salary.
sentences.chinese: 他昨天從我這兒借走的那本書花了我三分之一的工資。

sentences.english: At his death, he had lost about a third of his weight and had only a few dollars.
sentences.chinese: 他死時，體重銳減約三分之一，而且身上只剩幾文錢。

sentences.english: More than one-third of exploratory wells came up dry.
sentences.chinese: 三分之一強的探勘井都是乾井。

sentences.english: Over one third of all child deaths are linked to malnutrition.
sentences.chinese: 所有兒童死亡中三分之一以上與營養不良有關。

sentences.english: One thirds of the water is dirty.
Only one-third of the price is required of the student body.
sentences.chinese: 上海公安博物館對學生團體實行三分之一票價。

sentences.english: More than a third of the workforce is now part-time or temporary employees.
sentences.chinese: 現在超過三分之一的工人成爲兼職工或者臨時工。

sentences.english: Papers that are late will be penalized by one-third of a letter grade for each day late.
sentences.chinese: 報告遲交，每遲交一天將扣字母三分之一級。

sentences.english: Please fill about a third of this container with urine.
sentences.chinese: 請解小便到杯內約三分之一處。

sentences.english: Ni-MH batteries cover one third of such batteries.
sentences.chinese: 這些電池中鎳氫電池超過了三分之一。

sentences.english: One third of the pawpaw is for the dish, the remainder is for you.
sentences.chinese: 這個木瓜三分之一用來做菜，其餘的都是你的啦。

sentences.english: He spends nearly one third of his monthly income （in） buying books.
sentences.chinese: 他把每月收入的三分之一用來買書。
